      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with character? This vehicle is ready for the road and offers a solid foundation for its next owner! While it shows some honest signs of wear and age both inside and out, it remains a functional and spirited ride that still has plenty of miles left to give. It's a great opportunity to own a reliable car at a budget-friendly price point!",
