      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how beautiful this ride is\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it's looking absolutely flawless inside and out. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
