    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with Turner plates to ensure structural integrity. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and original dampers. Zero leaks, consistent compression across all cylinders, and a factory-spec limited-slip differential provide a visceral, linear power delivery. Finished in Alpine White over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with no evidence of oxidation or road rash. A rare opportunity for the purist seeking a mechanically synchronized, high-revving masterpiece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
