    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This pristine example of automotive excellence has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, presenting in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. The exterior retains its original, high-gloss luster with a deep finish entirely free of stone chips, swirling, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, devoid of any creasing or wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The undercarriage is equally impressive, showing no signs of weather exposure. This vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. It comes complete with a full documented service history, all original keys, and the factory window sticker. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
